nodes.text: Tookreek's Cantina, also known as the Tookreek cantina, was a cantina located in Dreviad Outpost in the Jundland Wastes of the desert planet Tatooine during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. It was named after its owner, the male Kadas'sa'Nikto Tookreek.
